     <div type="encomium">
   <head>R. S. His good-speede to the Herball.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>TRuely thou dost the world disclose,
which growes,</l>
      <l>Promiscuous; here a Thorne, &amp; there a Rose.</l>
      <l>So shall blacke vices vgly face
adde grace,</l>
      <l>Vnto the vertue, which shines next in place.</l>
      <l>So when a stinging Thorne shall wound,
is found,</l>
      <l>An Herbe to heale the Soule, and make it sound.</l>
   </lg>
</div>
